  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个Alice和John之间的通话时序图，场景是Alice先发起问候，问John近况如何，然后确认对方是否能听到自己。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Alice",
        "John",
        "问候消息"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，那Alice的第一条消息是同步调用还是异步？还有，\"how are you\"这条和\"can you hear me\"这两条消息之间，John需要立即响应吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Alice",
        "John",
        "消息类型"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "两条都是Alice主动发起的，所以都用实线加实心箭头表示调用。John的回复可以等两条都发完再统一回，用虚线箭头表示返回。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Alice",
        "John",
        "实线实心箭头",
        "虚线箭头"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把Alice到John的两条调用画好，第一条是\"Hello John, how are you?\"，第二条是\"John, can you hear me?\"，都用实线实心箭头。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Alice",
        "John",
        "Hello John, how are you?",
        "John, can you hear me?"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，这样很清晰。然后John回复两条消息：先回应能听到，再说自己感觉很好。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "John",
        "Alice",
        "回复消息"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "收到，我加上John返回的两条虚线箭头：第一条\"Hi Alice, I can hear you!\"，第二条\"I feel great!\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "John",
        "Alice",
        "Hi Alice, I can hear you!",
        "I feel great!"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，第一条问候消息前面是不是应该标注一下场景？比如\"in Sub\"表示这是在子流程里？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Alice",
        "John",
        "in Sub",
        "Hello John, how are you?"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "好的，我在Alice的第一条消息前加上\"in Sub\"标注，现在变成\"in Sub Hello John, how are you?\"，这样场景更完整了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Alice",
        "John",
        "in Sub",
        "Hello John, how are you?"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完美，这样整个通话流程就完整了：Alice先发起子流程问候，确认通信，John再逐一回应。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Alice",
        "John",
        "in Sub",
        "Hello John, how are you?",
        "John, can you hear me?",
        "Hi Alice, I can hear you!",
        "I feel great!"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
